snippet.title: Java Currency Formatter - HackerRank Solution Practice Program
snippet.description:
New course coming soon! Learn Java Fast launches on July 1st, 2020. Stay informed and join the waitlist: https://course.alexlorenlee.com/courses/learn-java-fast

- The solution to the Java Currency Formatter HackerRank program requires you to use a special method from the NumberFormat class. Just chuck that in your program and set it up for the 4 languages.

The best programmers practice, I'm glad you were able to practice with me today :)

I hope you enjoyed this solution to the java practice program on HackerRank for the Java Currency Formatter!

Hope you had a great Christmas :) -
